{"tid":1927160,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"國際文宣要文-將你想同世界講嘅說話寫出嚟","createTime":"2020-03-15T15:06:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T13:26:47.000Z","uid":190940,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bb263580d4d558eab91423661f2218638bdc1db7","tid":1927160,"uid":190940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T15:06:56.000Z","msg":"有朋友喺美國讀大學，做緊一個project係整一本雜誌，之後係會發行當地州免費派發。<br />\n雜誌其中兩個topic係Identity同time<br />\n佢想將呢一篇公開比手足投稿，將你想同世界講既說話寫出黎，佢會翻譯做英文，英文叻嘅巴絲可以幫手。<br />\n中文原稿都會刊登，唔想出名可以匿名，寫完留低筆名/tg真名。大家可以集思廣益造靚一篇，或者百花齊放，佢揀一篇黎貼都無問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n題目：identity(身分）或time(時間、時期、時代）<br />\n字數：大約五百字(英文要一版雜誌，唔知1:1對英文得唔得)<br />\n截止時間：21/3/2020（仲要排版同翻譯，明白有啲趕)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝手足，好人一生平安"},{"pid":"f5a43d4d1269233dfec66928f843de12d5dad504","tid":1927160,"uid":266548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T15:08:04.000Z","msg":"pish<br />\n<br />\n作者：透過控制議題，你就能主宰一個地方的政治議程。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1927089\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1927089</a>"},{"pid":"7abcee1d3f55d2df950aab1527f83db16b1b4df3","tid":1927160,"uid":190940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T21:27:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果寫緊留個comment等你"},{"pid":"a0c70344934e41bdf4061db2a3c77eeb373b4de7","tid":1927160,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T00:31:32.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"c3ca0c4b75f3bc16a4362e681867c6a64dc74324","tid":1927160,"uid":183576,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T00:32:38.000Z","msg":"準備動筆 寫完俾你"},{"pid":"0478965ec0fd7401fca7dfcb821dd0322f6ab2b8","tid":1927160,"uid":190940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3ca0c4b75f3bc16a4362e681867c6a64dc74324","tid":1927160,"uid":183576,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-